data.description: This immaculate home will have you will immediatly wanting to spend your next holiday here. You will notice its beautiful curb appeal as you drive up. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is move in ready and offers updates throughout. This home has ceramic wood flooring and tile throughout. The kitchen offers white cabinets and stainless steel appliances, which includes a gas range stove. The master bedroom has an en suite with two seperate closets, a custom shower and a granite top vanity. The additional bedrooms and bathroom are on the opposide side of the home as well as the laundry room. The backyard is great for entertaining, it is spacious and fully fenced in. Another plus to this home is the huge shop that you can use for all your projects. The entire shop is insulated with spray foam, has a/c, built in fans and electricity. The shop is also set up for 220 plug. Another storage area is located right off of the carport. Last but not least, there is a covered area for your camper or boat. Schedule your showing now and make it your own before the next holiday.
